data.description: NEW PRICE. Beautiful READY NOW 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in incredibly convenient Brightwood Farm. Completely FLAT extra wide driveway and front yard overlooked by ROCKER FRONT PORCH on a gorgeous CUL-DE-SAC lot with so no thru traffic in front.   Rear yard is equally incredible, GIANT rear concrete patio with PERGOLA and BISTRO LIGHTING, convenient STORAGE BUILDING and tons of private space. Backs to the woods and adjoining golf course, not to other homes. The interior is where it comes together. Mudroom built ins in the entry, formal living room, and BEAUTIFUL kitchen. GRANITE COUNTERS, STAINLESS APPLIANCES, tile backsplash and 42" mocha  cabinets. Breakfast area and HARDWOOD FLOORS on the main level. Fireplace, GIANT primary suite complete with separate shower and TUB plus dual vanities in BOTH upstairs baths. Large secondary bedrooms & located by highways, shopping, exercise, restaurants, and more. HOA's include POOL, multiple tennis courts, and FITNESS CENTER.
